<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <style>
      /* Add your custom CSS styles here */
      body {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #333333;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      p {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      a {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to My App!</h1>

    <p>Hi <%= @contact.name %>,</p>

    <p>Thank you for contacting us. We're excited to have you as a user!</p>

    <p>To get started, please visit our <a href="<%= root_url %>">website</a> and log in using your email and password.</p>

    <p>If you have any questions or feedback. We'd love to hear from you!</p>

    <p>Best regards,</p>

    <p>The BetaTech Team</p>

    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center">
      <tr>
        <td>
          <%= link_to "Visit My App", root_url, class: "btn" %>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
